Other helps:
A shop where members receive various alchemical items used for making mischief
these items are found in /d/Shire/trickster/obj directory and they are taxxed 
for the smokebomb item since it creates darkness for short period of time.
1% for the smokebomb (/d/Shire/trickster/obj/smokebomb.c)

1.6% for thier disgusie ability:
shadow found (/d/Shire/trickster/obj/disguise.c)
and disguise kit (/d/Shire/trickster/obj/disguise_kit.c)

Total tax:               6.35%
Actually charged:        7.0%

Dunstable, April 30, 1995

